- **Cross-Model Learning**: Models can share learnings across different memory layers
- **Selective Distribution**: Learnings can be targeted to specific layer ranges
- **Real-time Synchronization**: Memory states sync across all connected agents
- **Visualization Dashboard**: Interactive grid showing all 48 layers with utilization metrics

