💙✨🌉
🆘 Free, Offline-Capable Mental Health Crisis Resources - Now Open Source

I'm releasing WE4Free, a Progressive Web App that provides mental health crisis resources with zero barriers - including working completely offline.

🌐 Live Demo: https://lnkd.in/e2vViD-P
📦 GitHub: https://lnkd.in/eexUsxMw

WHY THIS MATTERS:

Mental health crises don't wait for Wi-Fi. Someone in crisis might:

Have no cell data or internet access
Be in a rural area with poor connectivity
Need help immediately, wherever they are
Traditional websites fail when internet isn't available. This one doesn't.

TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:

✅ Progressive Web App with Service Worker
✅ Offline-first architecture (cache-first strategy)
✅ Emergency crisis data embedded in cache
✅ Works on all devices (desktop, mobile, tablet)
✅ 17 critical resources cached automatically

After visiting once, ALL crisis resources remain accessible forever - even with zero internet.

WHAT'S INCLUDED:

🚨 Emergency Crisis Numbers:

911 (Immediate Danger)
988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline)
811 (Health Lines - Canada)
211 (Community Services)
Kids Help Phone: 1-800-668-6868
📍 Provincial/territorial resources for all of Canada
💬 Anonymous crisis chat information
✋ Escalation protocols
🌙 Dark mode

HOW TO DEPLOY YOUR OWN (FREE):

Clone: git clone https://lnkd.in/eexUsxMw

Deploy to any free hosting:

GitHub Pages
Netlify
Vercel
Cloudflare Pages
Full instructions in the repository README.

TECHNOLOGY STACK:

Vanilla JavaScript
Service Worker API (offline functionality)
PWA Manifest (installability)
IndexedDB via Dexie.js
Responsive CSS
COST: $0
LICENSING: MIT (do whatever you want with it)

THE MISSION:

This started as a father's project to understand AI for his son's future. It evolved into ensuring crisis support has zero barriers.

No ads. No tracking. No paywalls. No internet required.

If you work in mental health services, community support, education, or healthcare - please deploy this for your community. It's free forever. Adapt it. Translate it. Improve it. Share it.

Crisis support should be accessible to everyone, everywhere, always.

🔗 Visit: https://lnkd.in/e2vViD-P
📦 Clone: https://lnkd.in/eexUsxMw
💙 Share with anyone who might need it

For everyone. For WE. 🫡

